title: Dave Matthews Band Warehouse 2000-2012
description:
This is a collection of Warehouse yearly releases by Dave Matthews Band. It is given to members of the Warehouse Fan Association. The included albums are the ones that were given to senior members with at least 3 years of membership which includes an extra three songs.
I am uploading these in anticipation of the release of the 2013 package coming soon. I will upload that as soon as I have my hands on it. 

All albums are either MP3 256kbps or 320kbps and have correctly tagged files with album artwork.

2000 The Warehouse 5 Vol. 1
2002 The Warehouse 5 Vol. 2
2003 The Warehouse 5 Vol. 3
2004 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 1
2005 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 2
2006 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 3
2007 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 4
2008 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 5
2009 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 6
2010 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 7
2011 The Warehouse 8 Vol. 8
2012 The Warehouse 10 Vol. 1
